$interpreted: Boy: Mommy, the doll's eyes are lighting up~
Boy's Mom: My Lord, what a disgusting looking doll! Don't touch that!
Boy's Mom: Hey, you! Don't put that frightening trash pile on the side of the road!
Boy's Mom: What a disgrace. No concern for the environment...
Buff Sailor: #%@! Mind yer business lady!!
Wussy Sailor: Did the ferry to the Mechanical Territory dump all this?
Buff Sailor: Who cares, buddy!? We've got to take it to the dump anyway!
Buff Sailor: Hey, watch it!!!
Clark: Forgive me, sir. I wasn't paying attention...
Clark: Eh? You are sailors?
Buff Sailor: What's it to you bucko!? You lookin' for trouble?
Clark: Of course not, young fellow. I'm looking for a ship to the Mechanical Territory...
Wussy Sailor: The ferry? That's been out of operation for some time already. The taxes are just too high now. None of the merchants want to do business with the MT.
Clark: Oh, is that so...? Quite the conundrum...
Clark: Eh!? What's that?
Clark: What an exquisite robot. Did it come from the Mechanical Territory?
Wussy Sailor: Must be. When we were out on the sea, we saw all sorts of trash like this that was thrown overboard by ships from the Mechanical Territory.
Clark: Trash...? This couldn't possibly be trash...
Buff Sailor: Look at this crap. Busted up like this, it's gotta be trash!
Clark: Indeed, it is quite "busted up". But if we could find the right parts...
Clark: Is it possible that I take this robot off your hands?
Buff Sailor: Take what you like. It'll save us a trip to the dump!
Clark: Okay, then. All the necessary parts have been replaced. Now, where's the on/off switch...
Clark: What the rotten banana is it doing in a place like this...? Where was the designer's head at?
Maria: Main Core restart complete, confirming user. May I ask what the user's name is?
Clark: ...What is a "Main Core"...? And what's a user?
Maria: May I ask what the user's name is?
Clark: Is the user name...my name?
Clark: My name is Clark Shot.
Maria: Hello, Master Clark!
Clark: Master? No, no, no. I'm not your master. What's your name? What can you remember?
Maria: Maria has already successfully restarted her Main Core, Master Clark! Awaiting your next comm──
Clark: I can't...*sigh*...I'm tired.
Wussy Sailor: Did that robot just move?
Maria: Hello! My name's Maria! Model UPL-407 at your service~
Buff Sailor: Uhhh...this robot doesn't look like that piece of junk we pulled ashore...
Wussy Sailor: That thing's definitely worth a fortune...
Buff Sailor: Even though you fixed her, you have to give her back to us.
Clark: ...Didn't you say she was just trash?
Wussy Sailor: Well, we didn't know she could be fixed! We'll give you a repair fee, how's that?
Buff Sailor: Quit mouth farting! We were the ones who picked her up in the first place!
Clark: Do you recognize them? Would you like to go with them?
Maria: Maria doesn't recognize them! Maria wants to go with Master!
Clark: ...Okay, then. Let's go.
Buff Sailor: Aargh! So you ARE looking for trouble, eh?
Clark: I wouldn't have guessed you were also programmed to fight!
Maria: I will do my very best to protect my Master!
Clark: No, no. You don't need to...forget it.
Wussy Sailor: I've never seen such a refined robot before. You're basically like a human.
Buff Sailor: Mr. Waits is definitely gonna want that thing. Let's go! We've gotta tell the Bossman about this!
